 Ingredients of each white, capsule-shaped tablet include: The active ingredient - ranitidine (as hydrochloride) 300mg. Other ingredients include microcrystalline cellulose, croscarmellose sodium, magnesium stearate, hydroxypropylmethylcellulose (E464), triacetin and titanium dioxide (E171).
